{
  "blocks": [
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_6624a256ad39bdfb47f1c7c1",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "美好的一天",
        "text_hash": "8d8a775a9ed09c596e6cf2ab5e56048c4aa7b830a3687a2204dd906aa86ef263",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_0c39d74739666ddf70a07e46",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "Nicholas 在床上伸懒腰时，妈妈和宝宝向他打招呼。",
        "text_hash": "b4238a63bc502dfcfe84fcd49a0d7d40442cda3c87b85acca9f750360a1fe00d",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_3adf92bb55ba031813712408",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“多么美好的一天，”妈妈说。“醒醒，Nicholas。”",
        "text_hash": "addf8c84de05b77192337b7a4c95cb99a479093aa875b6c679ac94bda9a8aa31",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d4c25edd2b72d34f30d72983",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“你好，太阳，”Nicholas 说。“早上好，小鸟们。”",
        "text_hash": "02ae4d11e5568c71fc7cff4bd530fd8b9461fb183decdb970979626b5ca6d19b",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a9caf7fd5a369f3ac5e77f8b",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "爸爸和 Nicholas 坐在早餐桌旁。Nicholas 透过厨房窗户向他的朋友 Jacob 挥手。",
        "text_hash": "7765f1cb0457aca4fb1adb7559923c2c28830cddab94d97c9117d0f5f775ece1",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a0c5372a800f73fe09d6e369",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“今天天气真好，”爸爸说。“我们去河边野餐吧。”",
        "text_hash": "47b4e4485240f586f13c6eb2b9774073b511b392449447f231de2d856e7d6e5f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_1301f3aad7a2d9285c763485",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“我的朋友 Jacob 能来吗？”Nicholas 问。",
        "text_hash": "a5cb5eeb537485edcdc267e6d97198ce61504e502900fde36f3e5beb9db06d38",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_b1e7803229f8a0576bde47dc",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "动物们兴奋地跳上跳下。Nicholas 和 Jacob 互相搂着对方。",
        "text_hash": "c9e7a28eddc8c77de22dae36ab184d210266f9436dde6eeb39adc2f4eb625e9e",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_cd446f2c42c655dcd17d4ce8",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“别忘了我。我喜欢野餐！”Donkey 说。",
        "text_hash": "854c9c071ab719e617d3287bbfe61c5eacd982d98a3bfb03e717274ad2661541",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_5eeb3a0a3bbe4559474df930",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“还有我。我也想去！”Dog 说。",
        "text_hash": "61a5bea4b677aee37ebb5d3bb7982283866b0c912812c9a15fc74281b047a399",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_34480931c813811e043b535f",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“跟着我们，”小鸟们说。",
        "text_hash": "9ebf3303040f0cab6b801306e91dacc2bf222ce236c9bb2a4bc1e6853e64c17e",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_4fd65db2ee02ab00671f895f",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "爸爸头上顶着一个野餐篮。妈妈、孩子们和所有动物跟着他去野餐地点。",
        "text_hash": "f2e246628061093a4779788c70d835ba51bd6b3e79f06a2a8d0d2e706798fbda",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_f096af2ceb5cbeff59cd810b",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "Nicholas 和狗准备赛跑。",
        "text_hash": "708c5f73546d30b1744d83a7654fd8d5c81e39a1d538c61ac0204fc10b0255dc",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_7f03c1aa4e4387b432d47c4e",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“我要和你赛跑到那棵树那里，”Nicholas 说。",
        "text_hash": "f38982fd03670a1eb7dfd5689beec6cc02a436bafcc83bdf88bd42b86e279d47",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_5f0b1b2073df62cfba673093",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "到了树旁，Nicholas 弯下腰喘着气。",
        "text_hash": "570d34ead57a59f2a91c25ad4d1c6e07f8d714194a45fbadc54c26df76476c81",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_4fcff412c5ec474125b55831",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“我赢了，我赢了，”Donkey 说。",
        "text_hash": "dff8091873f48ccdc91e386e9374262c9795b3804fbb184777de8d9311f914e5",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_b9f0f20363ee79f22638dfb2",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“不公平，”Nicholas 说。“你有四条腿。”",
        "text_hash": "0302dd4a001a3b5b8071d552439682f6c034d24233c690c42626c9399172b57d",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_f233f9854d0cdb9d8868676e",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "Nicholas 做了一个倒立。Jacob 单手倒立。",
        "text_hash": "5c9a4c0185afdab9a78a887f24796916525059f352bf7eb9c0fd8f71aba85808",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_180227147f2a8b06cab935b0",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“看我会做什么，”Nicholas 说。",
        "text_hash": "b4d857bbcf9a2be65d75413370863d1dde7406963e7d9ac7d66d9dad6fd452f0",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_8683e42d6c16b6070424ff28",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“我打赌你做不了这个，”Jacob 说。",
        "text_hash": "ff286f3f5142b8be6d1468c19af462504c023a544742865138423ce9a7fa7272",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_0d0feaaeb6bab65271ff3abb",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "妈妈、爸爸和宝宝来到河岸。",
        "text_hash": "d5f9a0edd56f732743ea4c2e6ea7b89d3b0c10fdb0be6d19bbd2aab28bc56d00",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_2cf0b47d4da1ec39d470813f",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“这就是我们的野餐地点，”爸爸说。",
        "text_hash": "4aa70266878359635ffb334a4401f100af9f560efed31807d311c30b00fb90ae",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_f82347240bf03a19d1feb1de",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "Nicholas、Jacob、Donkey 和 Dog 跳进河里。",
        "text_hash": "54385a2125eabbb3328fbc79227ee33a6085298fa88ad8f889c64a1ccd43badb",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_bf06e73534219c95e6ca627c",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“和你赛跑到水里！”Jacob 说。",
        "text_hash": "347507d9199e9b978aacbd9dc88a1c9060c56a8e3c8e1a4cbd99d63000b97767",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_5d267e2e39e8bd897a620441",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "一家人坐在红白格子的野餐毯上，吃着他们的零食。",
        "text_hash": "36df68fde6ccfa0ab7b965bc2f2471616963a26956e262a9c88f55ed57378936",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_88871ca9f99c0f2bccc05feb",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“来吃东西吧，孩子们，”妈妈说。",
        "text_hash": "dc28b1bff52f8753c0184352b03adaf9e4c6cf8b6603c6566936a55802af3610",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a60dad3ae92642a88fa988e5",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "在 Jacob 家外面，Nicholas 向他的朋友挥手告别。",
        "text_hash": "2f3d0aa60817a5af119da589cb69c7af3298d557832ae4dab307d096fd5c9da7",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_354ffa06e3b31935d8695b41",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“该回家了，”妈妈说。“向 Jacob 道别吧。”",
        "text_hash": "4c18c44e32cd0088f9ecdacc448d77a0b9c24834079c1c26349d7b464b7af7d8",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_30d62779a41ba6b86f3b8016",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "Nicholas 和 Dog 在床上睡得很熟，而 Donkey 睡在外面的星空下。",
        "text_hash": "48c8192881340ad05100c8fa9222877252c25369540ad1790b4d0b21ca233af5",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_5b943652759ccc72d5cd7046"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    }
  ],
